name: Outcasts of the Society by ZzzLabs

metadata.description: Mutant Sloths are an extension of the original Sleepy Sloth Society Sloth. They are a new breed of Sloth that have been genetically engineered to be more aggressive and more aggressive than their original form. The Sloth Society has championed the development of these new Sloth types and has championed the use of these new Sloth types in the world of the Sloth community.
